Charles E. Carroll wrote:
>
>>(One might argue that the application need not be retroactive: we might
>>think of the effect of the amendment as changing, in the present, the
>>value of the Proposals' attribute "length-of-VP". But at least in this
>>case, that argument won't quite work, since the effect will be to make
